Texts.Chs: 这^green;网络核心^reset;上面有个坐标。也许那里有什么很棒的东西。我已经把坐标输入到了SAIL上，看看这会指向哪里。
Texts.Eng: ...There...Are some coordinates on this ^green;cyber core^white;. Maybe there will be some ^orange;awesome things^white; there. I'll input the coordinates into SAIL and see where it leads to.

Texts.Chs: 与我战斗的那架巨型飞行物确实令人生畏。 它掉落了一个武器放大器。 也许我可以以某种方式利用它。
Texts.Eng: The giant aircraft that I fought was truly intimidating. It dropped a weapon amplifier. Perhaps I could make use of this in some way.
